---------------------------------------------------------------------
Person to person interactions and the general enviroment of DarkWind
---------------------------------------------------------------------
 
No one be it player, wizard, arch, demi, or god will be allowed to
use profanity across ANY channel.  If you feel the need to swear
to get your point across and cant think of any other way to do it,
then go somewhere else.
 
If it makes you feel better to degrade people, at least have the
courtesy to do it privately in mudmail.  No one is allowed to
degrade fellow players via public channels.  If you feel that
they have done something wrong mail them about it, don't post
it in public.
 
If your level 100 or higher this is even more important.  You
represent what players what to become.  If you come across as
a less than desirable person, it reflects on every one of us.
 
Infractions to this rule will be as follows.
1st offense.  Verbal, documented warning.
2nd offense.  Demotion to lowest level in your catagory.
3rd offense.  Demotion to level 100 if already a wizard, and
              demotion to level 1 if a player.
4th offense.  Removal and banisment of your character.
 
This is not something to be taken lightly.  We want a friendly
atmosphere around her for both players and wizards, and if you
are unable to abide by this rule, you will not be welcome here.
